Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:06.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Black Knight Onyx,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:11.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hereby decree that your temporary status is to be lifted,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:14.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and you are to become the fifth member\Nof the Great Generals from this day forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:18.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Signed, Demon Queen Echidna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:23.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He is a newcomer, yes, but\Na steadfast supporter of our cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:30.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And I can think of no man better suited\Nto extend a hand to humanity on our behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:34.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,With him our quest for the Philosopher's Stone may no\Nlonger be futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:38.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Adding a fifth to our Four Great Generals\Nmay pose some problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:40.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but I will discuss that with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:47.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know I've made the right choice with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:51.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dire news, Your Highness!\NThe Great Spirit Portal is closing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:56.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do we know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:01:00.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, but we've begun to run low on\Nthe rare crystal catalysts that keep it open!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:02.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:05.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Never did I think it would come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:12.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not at the very moment where\Nour future seemed secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:18.42,Song,,0,0,0,,Live, live on, with all your might
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:22.88,Song,,0,0,0,,Follow the light to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:36.75,Song,,0,0,0,,Betrayed and left behind in this lonely world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:42.29,Song,,0,0,0,,Fearing a tomorrow I've lost sight of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:45.46,Song,,0,0,0,,I search for the place I belong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:51.96,Song,,0,0,0,,My heart screams out, "I want to be needed"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:02:00.71,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to puzzle out these entwined identities, but can I trust them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:04.08,Song,,0,0,0,,Live, live on, with all your might
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:08.08,Song,,0,0,0,,Follow the light to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:11.58,Song,,0,0,0,,Even if you lose everything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:15.92,Song,,0,0,0,,Stay connected to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:19.63,Song,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:23.50,Song,,0,0,0,,But that's all right with me right now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:27.42,Song,,0,0,0,,I have to overcome and press on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:33.33,Song,,0,0,0,,So I can smile with you again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:46.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is a crisis situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:52.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Shutina, Lord Onyx, and myself,\Nthe Portal is stable--but only for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:54.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In its current state, it won't last longer\Nthan seven days, perhaps less.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:55.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:02:58.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily, save the cookies for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean you should switch to an apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:07.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Echidna, what'll happen if\Nthe Big Spirit Thingy closes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to return to the Demon World.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:09.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Once it closes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:16.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,we've no idea how long it will be before\Nanother is opened to bring troops through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It could be centuries, or millennia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:23.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All more time during which the Demon World suffers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:28.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We must decide upon our army's next plans\Nwithin these next seven days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:30.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shutina, what is your opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I believe we have two choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:36.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We could return to the Demon World\Nbefore the Portal closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Retreat, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:44.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Our current army consists mostly\Nof denizens of the human realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:49.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Since we cannot bring them with us,\Nwe will need to disband our army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Which means we'd have to go our separate ways, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:57.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't want us to break up!\NNot when we've all become such good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:04:00.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So retreat's Option 1. What's Option 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:05.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The second option is to immediately\Nmobilize our army, attack Renailles,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and take the Philosopher's Stone for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That seems out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:10.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I would say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As would I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:15.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Our current forces are far weaker than\Nthey were during our last campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:19.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Bringing them into battle would\Ncause only foolhardy bloodshed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:22.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,especially knowing the humans still have their\Ngreatest ally:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:24.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo Demonhart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If only we were rid of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:33.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lord Onyx. Have you ever fought the Hero Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, but I've heard stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:41.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I fought against him, one on one,\Nwith all of my might, and still I was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So this I can say with confidence:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He is a monster, a force to be reckoned with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:49.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If we engaged him as we are,\Nhe would wipe out every last one of our troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:53.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Obtaining the Philosopher's Stone would\Nbe the least of our concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:58.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I do not fear death. I left the Demon World\Nknowing I may die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I am not willing to lead others to that same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:07.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My decision is made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:11.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The army is to be disbanded,\Nand we will return to the Demon World.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:17.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shutina and I must return. I am the\NDemon World's leader, and she is my second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Returning without the Philosopher's Stone\Nwill inevitably lead to conflict over the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:29.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They all seem at a loss for words. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:34.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Echidna, I know you're worried\Nabout him, but he's actually--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:36.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We should just tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:37.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,N-no, we shouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:41.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's fine, I know. You needn't say anything, Shutina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:46.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We may be 300 years apart in age,\Nbut we've known each other for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:54.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You know more than anyone the faith and\Nhope I've put into the quest for the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time, Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:58.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know this decision weighs heavily upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's nothing of importance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:09.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for staying by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:15.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As the ruler of the Demon World--no,\Nas the solitary demon Echidna, I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:23.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, this is unseemly of me! A Queen should\Nnot show her subjects this much weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I must remain proud till the bitter end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:31.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We will need to start over to find\Na new method of saving our Demon World.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:38.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You want to better the lives of your people.\NYou told me this when we drank together, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes. One cannot maintain order in a barren wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:48.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I would use the stone to bring about warm sun,\Nlush greenery, clean air and water,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:51.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,the same with which the human world is blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:55.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Since I was young, I've studied and trained for that plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:59.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,all to become the Demon Queen\Nand travel to the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:04.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I held fast to those hopes and dreams,\Nknowing the Stone would grant my desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:10.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yet now, it all ends in defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:14.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,First, let me make one thing clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:18.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Stone is not an all-powerful wish-granting device.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:23.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It is an advanced engine from the Mechanical Age that\Nutilizes a micro black hole
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:25.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,to produce nigh-unlimited energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I cannot be sure it would grant your desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:36.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd imagine a detailed manual on its operation\Nis hiding somewhere in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:43.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Humans are looking for it too,\Nbut its antiquity has made it rather tough to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:48.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All the more reason for us\Nto seek peace with the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:52.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If we worked together to find\Nthis 'manual' of which you speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:55.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, that would be pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:08:02.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We would have to steal the Stone from them.\NOur peace would end in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:08.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In any case, it's far too late for us to consider this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You needn't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:14.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As far as I know, there are two\NPhilosopher's Stones in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:16.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:20.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes. You only need one to accomplish\Nyour mission, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:24.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That leaves one for the human world\Nand one for the Demon World.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:27.46,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Two Stones... Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:28.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Would that not be ideal for creating peace\Nbetween your two realms?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And could you cut the crap and look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where's Lord Onyx?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:37.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Echidna, keep turning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:43.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The situation's too dire, so I ditched my disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Listen closely, Echidna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.88,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Wh... Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:57.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,First, I'm sorry I had to trick you,\Nbut it was the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here's the real reason I joined your army:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:07.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see if you were truly worthy\Nof the Philosopher Stone's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I'd realized you weren't,\NI would have left right then and there,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:15.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but when we spoke over dinner and wine,\NI was convinced you were worthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:20.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What wine?! The last drink I had was\Nwhen I bared my soul to Lord Onyx...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:23.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where is he?! Where has Lord Onyx gone off to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:27.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know you have the ability\Nto bring order to the Demon World.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And if peace in your world means demons\Nwill stop bothering humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,then giving you the Stone will be more than worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:40.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, is Leo Lord Onyx?\NHas Lord Onyx been Leo this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:52.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see. So that was the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've been had.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:59.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Echidna, I know you're still processing\Nall this, but we're low on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:04.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know where the other Stone is--\Nthe one that isn't in Renailles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:10.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Die, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When I look back on that moment now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:20.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,back then, we were no more than\Nthe Hero and the Demon Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:38.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And the Stone will really,\NTRULY be where you're leading us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, really, truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:42.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You aren't leading us into some terrible trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Could you be any more skeptical?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:49.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you even realize how much\NI've helped your Demon Army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:53.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm WELL aware of how much you've 'helped' us,\Nyou blathering imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, after I so nicely explained it all,\Nyou ungrateful moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:04.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Echidna. Don't you have any other moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:07.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is the same thing you did\Nwhen I came for my interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shut up. Don't speak. Drop dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:11.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You knew this was the only way I could do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:17.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I had to join up under a false name and\Nearn my way to an audience with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:19.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't have let me join otherwise, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:22.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Never in a thousand THOUSAND years\Nwould I ever let you join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:26.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now go eat some poison mushrooms,\Nsuffer for three days, then die a rotten death!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How did I never realize it was you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:34.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know now there were countless instances\Nwhere I should have known it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Damn it all! I should have been more cautious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll bear this shame for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And what infuriates me most of\Nall is how you are right as rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:47.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,mere SECONDS after I hit you point-blank with Inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:48.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Echidna!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo's been of great service to the Demon Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:56.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Won't you allow him to join us?\NI owe him a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:58.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And y'know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:03.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo gave me lots of advice and\Nhelped make logistics so much easier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:04.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And you know what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:06.71,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,He greatly reduced my overtime hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:10.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Also, Echidna, the dining hall could definitely pay\Nthe staff a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:13.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My daughter Julietta is deeply grateful to him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:18.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's awesome! When we all work together,\Nwork gets done super fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I beg of you, please, show him mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:23.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's kind of an ass, but I don't see why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All right! Enough, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:34.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I shall make an exception and pardon you\Nfor your deception as Lord Onyx.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:41.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That aside, is there truly another\NPhilosopher's Stone outside of Renailles?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:42.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:46.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can find it in the Seshat Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:49.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Seshat Mountains? That's extremely close to here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:53.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's protected by a pretty powerful\Nguardian. Shouldn't be a problem, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:58.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If Leo is describing it as powerful,\Nthen how fearsome must it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This sounds too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:02.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We can do it if we all work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:04.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We will come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:10.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very well. I would prefer not to be left alone with\Nthis insolent fool, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let us go, then, to the Seshat Mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:24.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm cold! I'm so cold! I'm freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.83,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Lily is from the much warmer South.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.46,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Same with you, right, Edvard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:29.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. My scales will stave off the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh. So where is this Stone at?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:38.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just a little further, at the peak of that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm cold! I'm gonna freeze to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.63,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Amun, morph, alleg, warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:45.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm so warm now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:47.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Shutina!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:52.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're quite welcome. You'd do well\Nto study some magic yourself, Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:02.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stubborn fool. Why did you teleport\Nus partway? Why make us walk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why waste our precious time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:06.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wanted time to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:09.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Talk? What is there left to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Passing the torch, what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:15.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Philosopher's Stone's been my big project\Nfor ages, and it's gonna be yours soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:20.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be a good idea to hear more\Nabout it from the person you're replacing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:26.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very well, O Wise One. What wisdom do\Nyou have to share about the Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:32.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like I said before, the Stone isn't\Nsome magic item you can use to grant wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You understand that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:36.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:41.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know that planting it in the ground wouldn't cause\Ngreen fields to sprout overnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:46.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,turn water to wine, or anything fanciful like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:53.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Once you get the Stone, make peace with\Nhumanity and search for the manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:59.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A copy of the Akashic Engine Usage Manual\Nshould be hiding somewhere out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:02.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Without it, you won't know how to use the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:08.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Peace with humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:17.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To be completely frank, until a little while ago,\NI didn't think it was possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You understand, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:25.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We couldn't have stolen their most precious treasure\Nthen asked for peace and harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:31.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But after speaking with Onyx--well,\Nyou--my opinion changed completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:35.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know the story is just that, a story, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:36.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not just a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:42.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So don't worry. I know humans\Nand demons can live in harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:50.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But getting to that point is going to cost\Na lot of blood, sweat, and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:55.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How foolish of you to underestimate me, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:16:01.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am the Demon Queen Echidna,\Nthe most powerful ruler my world has ever known!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:06.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Blood, sweat, or tears, one by one,\NI will endure it all to bring peace to fruition!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:11.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That so? Glad to hear it. Makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:21.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That tone... He sounds so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:25.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope you can defeat\Nany mighty foe that stands in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:27.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like me. Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:28.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Impudent swine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:29.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ack, that's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Echidna, you ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Be thankful that was all I unleashed upon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:37.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Payback time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:40.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:43.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gah! Dammit, that's no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:49.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was worried about them for a moment,\Nbut I'm glad they're getting along so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That means we can be the FIVE Great Generals!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:55.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, if we all work together, we'll be as\Nstrong as A HUNDRED Great Generals!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:57.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As long as everything keeps working out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:01.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:02.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's something I've been wondering about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why do you know so much about\Nthe Mechanical Civilization?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:11.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was roughly three thousand years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:15.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,the same human civilization\Nthat King Belial invaded, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:18.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Were you a scholar before becoming a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:23.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not really. I was just born back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:26.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see, so you were born in the Mechanical Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:33.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If that were true, then he'd be\Nover three thousand years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:38.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did he use some form of magic to extend his lifespan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is this Hero even human?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:48.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When Belial attacked, humanity created\Nliving bioweapons called the Demonhart Series.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am the fifth in that series.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:53.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My design placed emphasis on\Nhyper-reactive skill improvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hyper... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:59.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I copy any and all abilities my opponents use\Nagainst me to develop my skills ad infinitum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:03.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am the result of three thousand years\Nof hard-won experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:06.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And the DH Series weapons don't die from old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:10.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We keep living on, and on, and on,\Nwhich for me, meant growing stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:14.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here I thought you'd be more surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:23.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It means you possess the strength of\Nuntold hundreds of thousands of soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:33.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Had I known just how powerful you were,\NI would have found another route to the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:36.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But despite what happened,\Nwe eventually found each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not so bad when you put it that way, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:40.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:45.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One can never understand destiny,\Neven fate as strange as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:47.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fate where, after defeating me in combat,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:52.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,the Hero inexplicably joins my army and\Ntakes me right to the Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:57.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All of the other DH Series weapons died off.\NI'm the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:03.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you've lost all your brothers\Nand sisters. My condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:09.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They've embedded one critical order\Nin our cores: "protect humanity".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:13.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Protecting humanity is my sole identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For thousands of years,\NI've fought to bring about peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:21.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And when peace came, I've wished\Nfor more danger, more war to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:24.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you a fool?! What would be the point in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:27.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you not enjoy your hard-won peace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:30.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right. I should enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:36.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My skill development functionality put my orders\Nand my feelings all out of whack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:38.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:46.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I get to thinking.\NAm I just holding humanity back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:54.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Humanity can function without a hero.\NAm I just doing this for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:58.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Am I forcing myself onto humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:05.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Without you, the human world would\Nmost certainly be under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure, this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:10.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But what about next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:15.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One day, humanity might be able\Nto take down a Demon Queen all on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:19.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When that day comes, I won't have\Na place to belong anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:23.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I'm breaking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:28.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And when I'm too far gone, I'll bring chaos to the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,just to give myself a reason to keep protecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:36.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll plunge the world into disaster, then pull it back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:42.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll become nothing more than a machine\Nthat saves the world, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:45.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd be worse than any Demon Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:51.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Before that happens, you know what\Nneeds to be done, right, Echidna?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:53.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:54.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:02.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What a splendid view. It's almost as if nature\Nis rewarding us for making it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:03.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I concur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:05.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where's the guardian?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:08.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're right, there's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There is no guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:21.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have the Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:28.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's the heart of the Demonhart Series. An infinite\Ngenerator, the Akashic Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:31.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That is the Philosopher's Stone you're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:34.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hold on. You mean to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:35.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:40.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you want the Stone, then kill me and tear out my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:47.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,'Tis I, former Hero Leo Demonhart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:52.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm a skilled swordsman and have mastered all\Narcane schools of magic, including black magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:55.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've even defeated the Demon Queen Echidna\Nherself in single combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:57.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am ready and raring to fight for your cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Though still but a temporary employee,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:02.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,as of this moment, I announce\Nmy resignation from the Demon Army
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:06.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and reiterate my desire to\Nexterminate humanity once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:11.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And I'll say this now: you don't get to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.92,0:22:17.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you try to run, I will descend from this peak\Nand kill every last human I find.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:20.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll even destroy the texts that tell you\Nhow to use the Philosopher's Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:21.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:26.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You told me you want to save\Nthe Demon World, right, Echidna?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.08,0:22:30.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You said you'd endure blood, sweat, and tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:34.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,to obtain the stone and bring peace to fruition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:37.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Blood, sweat, and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:40.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The time to prove your mettle is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:46.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you want the Stone, if you want to save the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:48.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,then stop me, here and now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:50.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,brave heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:51.21,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934.4,619.2)}{\an7}I Want to Quit Heroing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:41.04,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,57.6)}{\an7}Next Time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:41.04,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(217.6,223.2)}{\an7}I'll Save
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:41.04,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,273.6)}{\an7}the World,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:41.04,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(947.2,331.2)}{\an7}Even If
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:41.04,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(908.8,381.6)}{\an7}That Means
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:41.04,Caption-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(896,432)}{\an7}Destroying It
